rows.label: tlk000004_msg0001
rows.name:
It's a long road to the capital,
Fons Maim.

rows.label: tlk000004_msg0005
rows.name:
Take your time getting ready.
Just let me know when you want to leave.

rows.label: tlk000004_msg0006
rows.name:
There are a lot of monsters on the road,
so make sure you're well-prepared.

rows.label: tlk000004_msg0007
rows.name:
All set?
Alright then, let's make our way
to Fons Maim!
